summary_text: 1. My best friend pushed me into the lake. 2. We were on our annual summer camping trip. 3. She dared me to catch a frog by the water's edge. 4. I declined because I was eating a sandwich. 5. She snuck up behind me and nudged me into the lake. 6. She handed me the frog after I emerged from the water. 7. I laughed and promised her revenge.
